# Designs

## Specs-D1 Category Renderer Polymorphism
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/views/SpecsView.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A1

```typescript
const categoryComponents: Record<SectionType, Component> = {
  goals: GoalsTable,
  architecture: ArchitectureCards,
  designs: DesignCards,
  plans: PlansTimeline,
  tests: TestsCards,
  reviews: ReviewCards,
  reports: ReportDashboard,
}
```

| Event | Payload | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `toggle` | `{ id: string }` | Expand/collapse item detail |
| `jump` | `{ id: string }` | Navigate to linked spec ID |
| `edit` | `{ item: SpecItem }` | Enter edit mode for item |
| `status-change` | `{ id: string; status: Status }` | Update item status |
| `save` | `{ item: SpecItem }` | Persist edited item |
| `delete` | `{ id: string }` | Remove item from section |


